Titolo: The Forgotten Realms Deluxe Edition

Anno: 2006

Descrizione: The Forgotten Realms Deluxe Edition is a compilation of role-playing video games set in the Dungeons & Dragons campaign setting called The Forgotten Realms. This compilation was released in December 2006 and includes the Baldur's Gate series (excluding the Dark Alliance games), Icewind Dale series and the first Neverwinter Nights and their expansion packs.

